## Agent Marketplace Showcase — Complete

**36 source files** across 20 pages, 6 components, 3 layout shells, 4 CSS files.

### Structure
```
apps/showcase/agent-marketplace/
├── package.json, vite.config.ts, tsconfig.json, index.html
├── decantr.essence.json, DECANTR.md
├── .decantr/context/ (7 section files + scaffold + decorators)
├── src/
│   ├── main.tsx, App.tsx
│   ├── components/ (Button, Card, Input, Avatar, Badge, Toggle)
│   ├── layouts/ (TopNavFooterShell, CenteredShell, ChatPortalShell)
│   ├── styles/ (global.css, tokens.css, decorators.css, components.css)
│   └── pages/
│       ├── marketing/HomePage.tsx — Hero, Features, How-it-works, Pricing, Testimonials, CTA
│       ├── about/AboutPage.tsx — Hero, Story, Team, Values, CTA
│       ├── contact/ContactPage.tsx — Hero, Contact form + sidebar
│       ├── legal/ — Privacy, Terms, Cookies (prose)
│       ├── auth/ — Login, Register, ForgotPassword, ResetPassword, VerifyEmail, MfaSetup, MfaVerify, PhoneVerify
│       ├── chat/NewChatPage.tsx — Agent browse/dashboard with search, filters, 6-agent grid
│       ├── chat/ChatPage.tsx — Thread-based agent interaction with right sidebar metrics
│       └── settings/ — Profile, Security, Preferences, DangerZone
```

### Decantr Integration
- Scaffolded via `decantr init --blueprint=carbon-ai-portal --existing --yes`
- Uses **carbon** theme tokens (`--d-primary`, `--d-bg`, `--d-surface`, etc.)
- Uses **carbon** recipe decorators (`carbon-card`, `carbon-glass`, `carbon-code`, `carbon-bubble-*`, etc.)
- Uses `css()` atoms from `@decantr/css` throughout
- Follows the V3.1 three-tier context model (scaffold.md, section-*.md, decorators.md)
- All 20 routes from the route map are implemented
- `pnpm build` passes with **zero TypeScript errors**

